queryExamples.name: Find all NFL quarterbacks
queryExamples.query: MATCH (p:PLAYER)-[:PLAYS_FOR]->(t:TEAM) WHERE p.position = 'QB' AND p.sport = 'nfl' RETURN p, t
queryExamples.description: Returns all NFL quarterbacks and their teams

queryExamples.name: High-performing players by sport
queryExamples.query: MATCH (p:PLAYER) WHERE p.fantasyPoints > 200 RETURN p.name, p.team, p.sport, p.fantasyPoints ORDER BY p.fantasyPoints DESC
queryExamples.description: Returns top fantasy performers across all sports

queryExamples.name: Team depth analysis
queryExamples.query: MATCH (t:TEAM)<-[:PLAYS_FOR]-(p:PLAYER) RETURN t.name, COUNT(p) as player_count, COLLECT(p.position) as positions
queryExamples.description: Analyzes team roster depth and position coverage

queryExamples.name: Injury risk assessment
queryExamples.query: MATCH (p:PLAYER) WHERE EXISTS(p.injuryStatus) AND p.injuryStatus <> 'Healthy' RETURN p.name, p.team, p.injuryStatus
